happened a bit in our neighborhood

00:18:12.160 --> 00:18:15.770
or robbed, mugged or
approached to buy cocaine

00:18:15.770 --> 00:18:18.330
from our fellow neighbors.

00:18:18.330 --> 00:18:22.500
But I'll say lastly in closing is
that if you can imagine a world

00:18:22.500 --> 00:18:28.390 position:56%
as Dr. Edwards, one of my colleagues
has a great quote about her vision

00:18:28.390 --> 00:18:32.770
