00:26:01.210 --> 00:26:07.660
But we continue to live and
love and struggle and win.

00:26:07.660 --> 00:26:11.840
I still believe that the age for
which we write is the age evolving

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:16.340
out of the dregs of the 20th
century into a more human age.

00:26:16.340 --> 00:26:21.240
Therefore, I recognize that my
writing must serve a dual purpose.

00:26:21.240 --> 00:26:23.860
It must be a clarion
call to the values

00:26:23.860 --> 00:26:27.390
of change while it also
speaks to the beauty

00:26:27.390 --> 00:26:30.510
of a non-exploitative age.

00:26:30.510 --> 00:26:37.040
