00:37:44.850 --> 00:37:51.120
Again that acknowledgment
of who we O-W-E-D and O-D-E

00:37:51.120 --> 00:37:52.860
if I can make ode a verb.

00:37:52.860 --> 00:37:59.540
So I'll conclude with this response
to the question of what we see

00:37:59.540 --> 00:38:03.130
as the value of our endeavors
or at least how I hope

00:38:03.130 --> 00:38:05.820
that our work will be recognized.

00:38:05.820 --> 00:38:09.250
The Dark Room affirmed and
perpetuated the vital notion

00:38:09.250 --> 00:38:14.060 position:56%
of community among artists of color,
writers, visual artists, musicians,

00:38:14.060 --> 00:38:18.360
filmmakers, as well as the
enduring power and significance

00:38:18.360 --> 00:38:20.620
of our cultural traditions.

00:38:20.620 --> 00:38:23.980
We foster relationships among
artists across differences

00:38:23.980 --> 00:38:29.850
in career, status, generational
affiliation, geography, poetics.

00:38:29.850 --> 00:38:34.800
We advocated making room for more
voices, as many voices as possible

00:38:34.800 --> 00:38:36.810
in the national literary landscape

00:38:36.810 --> 00:38:41.080
and particularly more room
for marginalized voices.

00:38:41.080 --> 00:38:44.700
And we especially supported
exploration and celebration

00:38:44.700 --> 00:38:47.000
of the black literary tradition.

00:38:50.040 --> 00:38:57.080 position:56%
Varied and multifaceted as it is and
